+  -m "$SUMMARIZE_LLAMA_GGUF" \
+  --host 127.0.0.1 \
+  --port 8080 \
+  --alias qwen3-local \
+  -c 8192
+```
+
+Probe the server before running summaries:
+
+```bash
+summarize local-runtime probe llama-cpp --base-url http://127.0.0.1:8080/v1
+```
+
